      <p class="section-sub">Tell us your day — AI picks the perfect outfit from your actual wardrobe, factoring in live weather, your occasion, and your personal style.</p>
      <div class="wear-features">
        <div class="wf"><div class="wf-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div><div><div class="wf-title">Location & weather auto-detected</div><div class="wf-desc">No need to check the forecast. AI reads live conditions and adjusts every recommendation.</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf"><div class="wf-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg></div><div><div class="wf-title">Explains every pick</div><div class="wf-desc">AI tells you exactly why each item was chosen — and what it skipped and why.</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf"><div class="wf-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg></div><div><div class="wf-title">Gets smarter every day</div><div class="wf-desc">The more you use it, the better it understands your preferences, lifestyle, and body.</div></div></div>
